            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Ti</abbr><ex>berius</ex></expan> Caesar <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">divi Augusti f(ilius) Iuli n(epos) Augustus pont(ifex) max(imus) trib(unicia) pot(estate) XXXVI</supplied> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>imp</abbr><ex>erator</ex></expan> VIII c<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>o</abbr><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ul</ex></expan> V <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Τιβέρ<supplied reason="lost">ιος Καῖσαρ θεοῦ Σεβαστοῦ υἱός θεοῦ Ἰουλίου υἱωνός Σεβαστός ἀρχιερεὺς μέγιστος</supplied> <lb n="2"/>δημ<supplied reason="lost">αρχικῆς ἐξουσίας λϛʹ αὐτοκράτωρ ηʹ ὕπατος εʹ <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied>
            </ab></div></div>
